# ulog

A uri logger to demo postgresql's data types

## table creation

```
CREATE TABLE log (
	log_id bigserial primary key,
	log_uri text NOT NULL,
	log_description text,
	log_timestamp timestamp default NULL
);
CREATE TABLE log (
	log_id bigserial primary key,
	log_uri text NOT NULL,
	log_description text,
	log_timestamp timestamp WITHOUT TIME ZONE NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW()
);

ALTER TABLE ONLY log ALTER COLUMN log_timestamp SET DEFAULT NOW();
my_timestamp TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE NOT NULL DEFAULT NOW(),
```
